{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gobs of Glory </strong> - A turn based multiplayer RPG true to the 5e SRD ruleset. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">NOW IN CLOSED PLAYTESTING!!! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Check out our subreddit for updates or to request an access key. Open playtesting should start soon, click on the Request Access button and I'll open it up as soon as it's stable enough for a bigger test!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Outwit your opponents in tactical turn-based PvP and PvE combat. As you win battles your character will gain riches and experience which can be used to level up and buy powerful magical items. At the end of each arena season characters will be richly rewarded by their Incantor based on their rank and Glory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features online multiplayer PvP combat as well as PvE solo &amp; co-op modes. Play solo or as a team to develop complex tactics that you can take back to the tabletop for even more Glory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For Windows, Mac, Linux and iOS.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1556230?t=1740508939","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556230/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740508939","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556230/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740508939","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556230/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740508939","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":6